name: TANDUR
description:
My name is Vincent, an illustrator from Klaten, Central Java, Indonesia
this is my work journey in learning digital drawing since october 2021, this is the 4th minting at HEN - OBJKT
this time I made art about the traditional method of growing rice
what is called tandur "plant backwards" in Indonesian "Tanam Mundur"
a local wisdom of Javanese culture which is still preserved in my village
